                        <interp inst="t18430130-name-507" type="given" value="MARY ANN"></interp>MARY ANN MERCER</persName>
                  </hi>. This letter is not my handwriting—I know nothing about it—I did not authorize any one to write it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
